## Architecture (current thinking)

```
Customer observability stack (Datadog / Grafana / AWS)
        |
    Plugin install (OAuth, read-only)
        |
    Discovery agent
    Reads: logs, configs, IAM policies, network state, tickets
        |
    Mapping agent
    Maps regulation clauses to live signals
    Novel mappings → human review queue
    Validated mappings → evidence base
        |
    Operate layer
    Live dashboards, clause-named alerts, SOAR playbooks
        |
    Export layer
    Regulator-formatted audit package, full citation chain
```

LLM provider: Mistral or Aleph Alpha for regulated reasoning steps (EU data residency by architecture). Claude for non-regulated reasoning where appropriate.

