## ICP

**In:** Lean security and platform teams (2-5 people) inside European mid-market companies (200-500 employees) in regulated industries: fintech, healthcare, construction, public sector. Must face 3+ overlapping EU frameworks and currently spend €50k+ per audit cycle on consultants or equivalent manual labor.

**Out:** Companies with 10+ dedicated SecOps engineers, companies using only one regulation, US-centric companies already on Vanta or Drata.

---

## North Star Metric

**% of audit evidence that was auto-collected and audit-ready, per customer per quarter.**

- Baseline (manual): 10-20%
- Year 1 target: 70%+ for any regulation with an installed plugin

---

## Status

Currently in discovery and pilot design phase. Building toward an MVP scoped to `DORA x Fintech x Germany` on a reference stack of AWS + Datadog + Jira.

MVP launch criteria:
- 70%+ auto evidence coverage on DORA / fintech vertical
- 99%+ evidence accuracy verified against a labeled benchmark
- Under 24 hours time-to-first-evidence on reference stack
- 0% hallucination rate on regulator-facing output
- At least one paid pilot has passed a real audit with the exported package

